<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 6" captionStartId="F6" captionText="Figure 6. Distributions of A. crassifolius, A. insurae, A. longipetalus and A. pleurocarpus in peninsular Thailand. Only the region in peninsular Thailand is shown; adjacent areas in Peninsular Malaysia and Myanmar are removed." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.151.51643.figure6" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/422435" pageId="0" pageNumber="67">6</figureCitation>
) and probably Myanmar (see notes), in lowland rain forests.
</paragraph>
